## Key Concepts
- Docker Config rotation with versioned configs
- Rolling updates with update-parallelism and update-delay for zero downtime
- Graceful reload semantics (SIGHUP or /reload endpoint)
- Update order start-first to ensure new containers start before old ones stop

## Code Example
```javascript
// Node.js reload handler
const fs = require('fs');
let flags = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/etc/flags.json','utf8'));
process.on('SIGHUP', () => {
  flags = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/etc/flags.json','utf8'));
  // apply flags to runtime features
});
```

